  "description": "<p><strong>正值苹果App Store 5周年之际，拍卖巨头eBay 进行了一个有意思的小实验，研究人们离开各种应用之后到底“能不能活”。</strong>200名 “app-happy” 受试者参与了实验。首先，实验要求他们远离各种应用，自制4天；然后再允许他们使用应用，继续观察四天（如下图所示）。结果有1/3的人没有完成自制，其 中一位受试者甚至将其与戒烟相提并论。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e7fd21f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244309.htm&amp;t=eBay+%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244309.htm&amp;t=eBay+%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244309.htm&amp;t=eBay+%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244309.htm&amp;t=eBay+%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%83%BD%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244309.htm&amp;t=eBay+%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BA%94%