  "description": "<p>希捷今天发布了两款全新的企业级硬盘，其中<strong>3.5寸的“Terascale”面向需求低成本、低功耗、高密度的大规模数据中心，2.5寸的“Enterprise Performance 10K HDD v7”则针对关键任务应用。</strong>且不说别的，希捷硬盘现在的命名是越来越混乱了，完全不成体系，而且每每都特别长，真是吐槽无力，不知道想干啥。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e7fd21e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244308.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%96%E5%A8%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244308.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%96%E5%A8%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244308.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%96%E5%A8%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244308.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%96%E5%A8%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244308.htm&amp;t=%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%